{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_07_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 恋する少女、一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私をヒロインにした恋愛ゲーム……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making me the heroine of a romance game…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。ゲーム会社の持ち込み企画で、星見プロの\nアイドルを使ったゲームを作ることになったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's right. It's a project brought in by a game company\nto create a game featuring Hoshimi Prods.'s idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私がヒロインだなんていいんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But is it really okay for me to be the heroine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ヒロインはあくまで『一ノ瀬怜』という\nキャラクターだから、そんなに気負わなくて大丈夫だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The heroine is just the character \"Rei Ichinose‚\"\nso don't worry too much about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれませんが、自分がゲームに出ると思うと\nやっぱり恥ずかしいし、緊張します……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That may be true‚ but I still feel embarrassed and\nnervous thinking about appearing in a game…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私と疑似恋愛するゲームなんて\n楽しんでもらえるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will people really enjoy a game where\nthey pretend to have a romance with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーム会社の人達は「ぜひ怜で」と言っているし\nファンも怜の新しい一面を見られて嬉しいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people at the game company are insisting on starring Rei‚\nand I think fans will be happy to see a new side of Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。分かりました\nそれで私は具体的に何をすればいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. Understood.\nSo what specifically should I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7000022888,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8305.714241700003,
          "startTime": 60.0057165305
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームのスタッフから預かったんだが\nこの書類を見てくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I received this document from the game staff.\nWould you take a look at it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2267442345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "これは……アンケート、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… a survey?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛に関するアンケートだよ。ゲームのシナリオを\n作るに当たって、怜の恋愛観を参考にしたいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a survey about romance. They want to reference your views\non romance when creating the game's scenario.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0613514423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私の恋愛観がシナリオに反映されるんですか？\n分かりました、やってみます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will my views on romance be reflected in the scenario?\nUnderstood‚ I'll give it a try…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8000022888,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3343505999949,
          "startTime": 83.9333366394
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 83.8000022888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "怜、アンケートは書き終わったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ have you finished filling out the survey?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.16667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "週末にゲームスタッフと打ち合わせがあるから\nそれまでに提出してほしいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a meeting with the game staff this weekend‚\nso I'd like you to submit it by then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、まだ全然埋まってなくて\n書こうとはしてるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ but I haven't filled out much of it yet.\nI've been meaning to‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "理想のデートとか、恋人と何をしたいかとか\nあまり人に話したことがないので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Questions like ideal date or things like to do with my partner.\nI've never really talked about these things with anyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "改まって答えるのが恥ずかしいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you embarrassed to answer them formally?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……そうです！　恥ずかしいんです！\n私が恥ずかしがったらいけませんか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…Y-yes! It's embarrassing!\nIs it not okay for me to be embarrassed!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "だって、私の考える理想の恋愛が\nゲームのシナリオに反映されるんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because my ideal view of romance is supposed to be\nreflected in the game's scenario‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "私の妄想が世間に公表されるみたいで……\nこんなの恥ずかしいに決まってるじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like my fantasies are being made public…\nIt's embarrassing‚ isn't it obvious!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7000058492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも私は、ずっとダンス漬けの毎日で\n恋愛する暇なんてなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ I've been busy dancing all day‚ every day‚\nso I haven't had time for romance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8666725159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、好きな人が出来たら何をしたいとか\nあまり考えたことがなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I haven't really thought about\nwhat I'd do if I love someone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3168144059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……\nちなみに、アンケートのどの質問で悩んでいるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nBy the way‚ which question in the survey are you struggling with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "沢山ありますけど……例えば\n「理想のデートで行きたい場所は？」という質問です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many‚ but… For example‚\nThe question \"Where would you like to go on your ideal date?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "デートなんてしたことがないので\nどう答えたらいいか分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I've never been on a date before‚\nI don't know how to answer it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.200000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "普通はショッピングや映画館って答えるんでしょうけど\nそれが私の理想のデートかと言われると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ people would say shopping or the movies‚\nbut if you ask me that those are my ideal date…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8333340963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "『普通』に囚われなくていいんじゃないか？\nもっと素直に、怜が行きたい場所を書けばいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't feel limited to what's \"normal.\"\nYou should just write down where you'd genuinely like to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7623840646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私が行きたい場所……テーマパーク、とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where I'd like to go… Like a theme park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "テーマパークでデートか\n可愛らしくていいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A date at a theme park?\nThat's cute‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.700000763,
